{"tid":2377292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【油麻地封鎖區佈局】入境懲教海關消防  駐守病毒核心區域　警守病毒區最外圍","createTime":"2021-01-23T13:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T19:05:23.000Z","uid":103156,"like":232,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"0ff3d7fa2b951f90f5db60fca1d8dfb6a1e3a11f","tid":2377292,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XwXS3Y0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwXS3Y0.jpg&h=85b81113&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50d82f0c97257215893b309e973113845dac3763","tid":2377292,"uid":103156,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:14:57.000Z","msg":"油尖旺區持續爆發疫情，政府在今日（23日）凌晨 4 時宣布圍封油麻地區域，區內人士須持陰性檢測報告才可以離開其大廈，而任何人則不可離開指定區域（下稱圍封區域），即東至吳松街、南至南京街、西至炮台街、北至甘肅街。<br />\n<br />\n早前有報道指，有逾 3,000 公務人員在場處理封區事宜，當中不少是紀律部隊成員。入境、懲教、海關、消防各自駐守「受限區域」一部分，而警察則負責看守出入口及外圍巡邏。(立場新聞)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3836799259738999/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3836799259738999%2F&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TarJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=64e02146\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3836799259738999/</a>"},{"pid":"e134ff94d592f7067d6db65b6856812a96e14610","tid":2377292,"uid":79563,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:15:44.000Z","msg":"守城 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4e6e8d4cbe3748c80f0afe45072773effad260","tid":2377292,"uid":167506,"like":72,"dislike":2,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:16:02.000Z","msg":"離間 識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fc268a19e469357b2db6fa63efb386aade7